These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
3 different pets are kept: pony, ferret, mouse
The people have 3 different jobs:  architect, engineer, firefighter
1. the owner of the pony is in an even position##4
2. the architect is on the left or right of the firefighter##3
3. the architect is the owner of the ferret##1
4. the owner of the mouse is on the far left##1
5. the engineer is the engineer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Pet   | mouse | pony | ferret |
| Job    | engineer    | firefighter | architect |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, r&b, metal
The people use 3 different means of transport: boat, roller, taxi
1. the fan of electronic is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the roller is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the person driving the roller is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Music-Genre       | r&b | metal | electronic |
| Transport   | taxi    | roller     | boat        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: baking, photography, sudoku
3 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, monopoly
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
3. the person who's hobby is photography is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | photography | baking |
| Game   | scrabble | backgammon     | monopoly  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, sports, superhero
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, nurse, police-officer
1. the person watching sports movies is the nurse##1
2. the person watching musical movies is the police-officer##1
3. the person watching sports movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching superhero movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | sports  | musical  |
| Job         | dancer  | nurse | police-officer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, techno, electronic
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, dutch
1. the fan of electronic is between the fan of gospel and the canadian##2
2. the fan of techno is in an odd position##4
3. the dutch is on the left of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre         | gospel   | electronic | techno    |
| Nationality   | colombian | dutch     | canadian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, rose, iris
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cricket, lacrosse, tennis
1. the person who growsazalea is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
4. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Flower   | rose | iris | azalea   |
| Sport   | tennis     | cricket    | lacrosse |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
House: townhouse, futuristic, craftsman
3 different pets are kept: dog, goat, turtle
1. the futuristic house is on the right of the townhouse house##1
2. the townhouse house is between the owner of the turtle and the craftsman house##2
3. the townhouse house is on the left of the futuristic house##1
4. the owner of the dog is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| House   | craftsman | townhouse | futuristic |
| Pet           | goat         | dog         | turtle |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
3 different games are played: domino, mah-jongg, billiard
3 different pets are kept: frog, rat, snake
1. the owner of the frog is between the owner of the rat and the person playing domino##2
2. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Game   | mah-jongg | billiard | domino |
| Pet    | rat    | frog | snake     |

