.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, coffee, cola
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, action, thriller
1. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | 7up    | cola      | coffee |
| Movie-Genre       | action | thriller | fantasy   |

