1. the teacher is on the right of the lawyer##1
2. the owner of the rat is the journalist##1
3. the owner of the cat is the teacher##1
4. the teacher is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | lawyer | teacher | journalist |
| Pet   | chinchilla | cat   | rat |

