.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
City: london, nizza, edinburgh
3 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit
1. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to nizza and the owner of the pony##2
2. the person traveling to nizza is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the pony is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| City   | nizza | edinburgh | london |
| Pet     | goldfish    | rabbit  | pony   |

