.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, skateboard, motorbike
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: ambient, hip-hop, jazz
1. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the van##1
2. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
3. the fan of hip-hop is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
4. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Transport   | van  | motorbike     | skateboard |
| Music-Genre   | hip-hop | ambient | jazz    |

