2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
3. the art-deco house is in an odd position##4
4. the victorian house is on the left or right of the art-deco house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3   |
| Food          | watermelon | cucumber | kale  |
| House   | cape-cod      | victorian  | art-deco |

