.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-19::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: snowboarding, parkour, swimming
There are 3 different nationalities: american, argentine, thai
1. the thai is on the left or right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##3
2. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Sport      | snowboarding | parkour | swimming |
| Nationality   | argentine   | thai          | american |

