.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, hamster, turtle
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, blend, chaman
1. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
3. the owner of the turtle is in an even position##4
4. the blend-smoker is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | hamster  | turtle   | guinea-pig |
| Cigar   | chaman | blend | bolivar       |

 